#NEXUS
lore.subspaceparasite.beckon_si=§lEpithet:§r Venkrol §l|§r §oSeed structure that calls parasites like moths to a wound.
lore.subspaceparasite.beckon_sii=§lEpithet:§r Venkrol §l|§r §oThe call grows louder; the ground learns to answer back.
lore.subspaceparasite.beckon_siii=§lEpithet:§r Venkrol §l|§r §oBeacon and birthing room; the air tastes like copper and is thick like mud.
lore.subspaceparasite.beckon_siv=§lEpithet:§r Venkrol §l|§r §oAn address for the hive. Everything nearby is now an entrance, exit, and void.
lore.subspaceparasite.dispatcher_si=§lEpithet:§r Dod §l|§r §oFirst dispatcher; signals, orders, and others in tidy loops.
lore.subspaceparasite.dispatcher_sii=§lEpithet:§r Dod §l|§r §oChannels widen; traffic of limbs and messages never ceases.
lore.subspaceparasite.dispatcher_siii=§lEpithet:§r Dod §l|§r §oLogistics perfected and reinforcements arrive before you finish bleeding.
lore.subspaceparasite.dispatcher_siv=§lEpithet:§r Dod §l|§r §oThe hub and the highway; strike it down or watch a living continent converge.
lore.subspaceparasite.rooter_si=§lEpithet:§r Leem §l|§r §oSeeded structure meant for enduring the pain of other parasites in it's place.
lore.subspaceparasite.rooter_sii=§lEpithet:§r Leem §l|§r §oSeeded structure meant for enduring the pain of other parasites in it's place.
